<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((المشكاة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٨٤٥)</span>، <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٤٦٤)</span>، <span class="c2">((صحيح أبي داود)</span>) <span class="c2">(٨٦٣)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>